      "content": "I hear how desperate it is to feel like the only solution is to disappear, and I want you to know that this isn't a failure of logic but a symptom of the overwhelming pain you are in. When the world feels like it has collapsed, the mind often mistakes the feeling of being a burden for the actual reality, leading to thoughts that stopping the pain means ending oneself. Please, do not make the decision to leave based on this feeling; instead, reach out to a crisis hotline or a trusted professional who can listen without judgment and help you see that there are other ways to survive this darkness.",
